                                                                  Data="M12,3 C7.03,3 3,7.03 3,12 C3,16.97 7.03,21 12,21 C13.9,21 15.66,20.41 17.11,19.4 L20.6,20.4 L19.6,16.91 C20.58,15.47 21,13.76 21,12 C21,7.03 16.97,3 12,3 Z M8.1,11.1 C8.62,11.1 9.05,11.53 9.05,12.05 C9.05,12.57 8.62,13 8.1,13 C7.58,13 7.15,12.57 7.15,12.05 C7.15,11.53 7.58,11.1 8.1,11.1 Z M12,11.1 C12.52,11.1 12.95,11.53 12.95,12.05 C12.95,12.57 12.52,13 12,13 C11.48,13 11.05,12.57 11.05,12.05 C11.05,11.53 11.48,11.1 12,11.1 Z M15.9,11.1 C16.42,11.1 16.85,11.53 16.85,12.05 C16.85,12.57 16.42,13 15.9,13 C15.38,13 14.95,12.57 14.95,12.05 C14.95,11.53 15.38,11.1 15.9,11.1 Z"/>
